                    <locus target="#iir(ecto) #iiv(erso) #iii r(ecto) #18r #38r #118r #137r"/> and <locus target="#179v"/>: blank
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e03">
                    <desc>
                    The hand is well trained and there are several beautiful illuminations which appear authentic
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e04">
                    <desc>
                    Identified in the insurance hand list as Psalter 20
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e05">
                    <desc>
                    Psalm 118 contains the spiritual meanings of the Hebrew letters, several of which are unique
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e06">
                    <desc>
                    Scribal intervention:
                    words of text are written interlinearly (<locus target="#1r #2v #3r #19v #20r"/>, etc.);
                    and lines of text are written interlinearly (<locus target="#6v #55v #66r #73r #78r"/>, etc.);
                    and interlinearly with a symbol (┴) marking the location where the text is to be inserted (<locus target="#31v"/>, line 3);
                    text has been removed (<locus target="#16r #50r"/>)
                    </desc>
                    </item>
